        SayNode(character: "ar", dialogue: "「香烟你不喜欢所以被排除了，嗯……不，或许刚刚的“香烟”也可以算在里面。」", pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
