        SayNode(character: "me", dialogue: "「要是真的有吸血鬼的话，还是希望和GALGAME里一样啊~要是金发双马尾就好了~啊！刚才你也说过这个吧！可爱的吸血鬼！GALGAME里是有的！」", pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
