        SayNode(character: null, dialogue: "准确来说，我并没有完全夺下那块“铁片”——虽然我仍然还不清楚那是什么，然而手中的触感让我想到了“金属制成的片状物”。", pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
